{"word":"μέσφα","slug":"μέσφα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μέσφα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>poetic for <a href='S:μέχρι'><el>μέχρι</el></a>\n<p/><i>until</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>μέσφ' ἠοῦς</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; with <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <el>μ. ἐχθές</el> <i>till</i> to-morrow, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/>"}]}